results.description:
White Rock lake, Sunset Bay
Comorant Fishing Party
Double-crested cormorants are highly social and tend to congregate in large numbers.  They will engage in cooperative fishing where a large group will work together to herd the fish into a small area where they are easy pickings.  This was one small section of a very large fishing party of cormorants.
